|---------------------------------------------------|
|   .............BEFORE PROCEEDING...............   |
| Download and install MESA v7503 by following the  |
| instructions on                                   |
| http://mesa.sourceforge.net/prereqs.html#toc-1-6  |
|---------------------------------------------------|

|---------------------------------------------------|
|   ...........HOW TO USE THESE FILES............   |
| The contents of MESA_files/mesa_source directory  |
| should replace the following files in the user's  |
| copy of MESA v7503.                               |
|---------------------------------------------------|

  mesa/atm/public/atm_def.f90
  mesa/atm/private/table_atm.f90

  mesa/const/public/const_def.f90

  mesa/data/net_data/nets/mesa_49.net
  mesa/data/atm_data/*

  mesa/star/private/init.f90
  mesa/star/public/star_lib.f90
  
|---------------------------------------------------|
| Next, cd into mesa/atm, mesa/const, and mesa/star |
| individually and do ./clean, ./mk, and ./export   |
|---------------------------------------------------|

|---------------------------------------------------|
|   ..............HOW TO RUN MODELS..............   |
| To run MESA models using the included inlists and |
| run_star_extras.f, the user must place            |
| run_star_extars.f in work/src, then do ./clean    |
| and ./mk in the work directory to recompile.      |
| In the inlists, the following input fields need   |
| to be replaced with the desired values:           |
| <<H1>> <<H2>> <<He3>> <<He4>>                     |   
| <<MASS>> <<BC_TABLE>> <<HISTORY_NAME>>            |
|---------------------------------------------------|
